examples: It's a pity our trips to New York don't coincide.
Es una pena que nuestros viajes a Nueva York no coincidan.
The strike was timed to coincide with the party conference.
La huelga se programó para coincidir con la conferencia del partido.
The singer's arrival was timed to coincide with the opening of the festival.
La llegada del cantante se programó para coincidir con la inauguración del festival.
The interests of employers and employees do not always coincide.
Los intereses de empleadores y empleados no siempre coinciden.
